key.name: How may I help you?
If I'm going to get into Team Mushroom, I've got to study hard!
I want to be best friends with all kinds of monsters. That's what Team Mushroom is all about, right?
How may I help you?
$npcName:11003501[gender:1]$ and I wanna be bigshots in Team Mushroom someday. But it'd be cool to work for Dryad Co., too... What should we do?
The Team Mushroom is a huge organization, you know!
What is it?
The Team Mushroom has people all over the world. You'll find them wherever you find monsters!

Team Mushroom and Dryad Co. don't have much in common. Dryad sells the tools of the pet-taming trade. Team Mushroom is working to protect the world from devastation, and unite all peoples across the nation!
I work alone, but I'll be in need of a partner in the future.
What about me?
Hey... Are you serious...?
Not right now. But... maybe later.
What is it?
You the man, Ducky. Well... You the duck.
Slime, you're mine.
There are lots of hungry $itemPlural:61000002$ here. I'm here to capture one as a pet.
Who's your little friend?
Did you come here alone?
This is my $item:61000005$. We're traveling together. Say hello, $item:61000005$.
Hello, Duckling.
Why are you traveling with a duckling?
No, it's just me and my $item:61000005$ on the open road! Though I did bump into my childhood friend $npcName:11003506[gender:1]$. Small world, isn't it?
I guess my little $item:61000005$ is feeling shy.
$item:61000005$ and I are training. I'm going to be a great pet master someday!
See the hungry $itemPlural:61000002$ over there? This place is getting crowded because of them...
You're way too green to cut it in Team Mushroom.
Tamed monsters are called 'combat pets.' Don't forget that, 'cause it might be on the test!
Do you need more candy packs?
Ever since those hungry $itemPlural:61000002$ showed up, this place has been overflowing with tourists. I actually ran into a childhood friend the other day!
What is it?
I'm a member of Team Mushroom, but I'm also a freelance pet-tamer.
Can I hire you?
Not now. I'm on vacation.
Apparently, Dryad Co. set their R&D department loose on monsters' tastebuds and developed these new monster candies. The $itemPlural:63000000$ are pretty popular.
Where can I get these monster candies?
Tell me about Dryad Co.
Most major supply shops should carry $itemPlural:63000000$. I'm pretty sure $npcName:11003506[gender:1]$ has some in stock.

I don't really know much, myself. It's a tech giant with lots of next-gen products. Rumor has it one of the founders of Dryad Co. recently retired, but nobody really knows much about them, or even what they look like.
Can I help you?
My parents ran this store before my brother inherited it. And now he's chasing his dream of turning it into a cafe or something...
The cafe's being remodeled right now. You should swing by when it reopens!
Ah... Hello...?
Ah... Hello...? I want to make some monster friends...
Let's get to business.
It's great having friends to hang out with.
I used to work with a friend who loved monsters. I helped my friend's dream come true...
There are no bad monsters.
Why not take a stroll with a little friend?
Ducky!
Quack...?
Quack...?
What's happening?
Lookit me!
What's happening?
Uh... Uh uh...
Can I help you?
We aren't open yet. Can you please come back later?
Of course.
When are you opening?
Who runs this place?
What's that music?
We... don't have a date yet, actually. The boss wants to redecorate and... and hire more people.
Watch your step. It's slippery over there.
It seems the boss has strange tastes. He asked me to wear this outfit, even though we aren't open yet. It's so uncomfortable...
Isn't it cool? It's the $map:61000008$ theme song! The boss doesn't like it, but it's pretty popular these days.
Come to think of it, didn't the boss lose a game of $map:61000008$ the other day...?
What is it?
Doo doo doo, la la la!
Mm-hmm, lala-lalala!
Sh. I'm trying to think of a melody. Can you give me a minute?
Yeah, goodbye.
(Wait.)
♬ Compelled to capture every pet! You and I, together! ♬
Yeah, goodbye.
(Wait a little more.)
♬ I wish for unparalleled skill... ♬
A fan, are you? Want my autograph? An advanced copy of my album? Well, it's coming out soon, so you'll just have to wait!
I'd like to hear a song.
I want to know about your pet.
My new song is a secret! You'll have to wait for the single, like everybody else.
This one... this one cannot be tamed. It's special.
Where can I get one?
That's my secret!
Grrr...
Grrr...
(It's locked.)
(It's locked.)
What is it?
Don't trust everything you see.
How did I end up like this?
Don't you want the power of the Devil Tree?
Mushrooms make mistakes, too...
I don't feel like chatting today...
Such is the life of a mushroom.
I don't feel like doing anything today...
Heheh, want to play with me?
Heheheh... I've got something real fun cooked up for those humans.
Heh heh heh.
Heh heh heh heh.
